measurements.description: Forty-five flowers and 18 buds on five upright inflorescences up to 10cm; dorsal sepal curved forward, lavender; lateral sepals slightly cupped, lavender, fading to white at margin; petals cupped, lavender outside, streaked white and lavender inside; lip broad, flat, trilobed, dark lavender, lighter shade at the margin; substance good; texture matte.
